        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "A rare genetic retinal disorder characterized by childhood-onset of markedly delayed visual adaptation to both dark and light conditions marked difficulties tracking moving objects and mild photophobia. Visual acuity is variably reduced while color vision is unaffected."
